title: Young and Scrappy
description:
Join Sadie Robertson Huff as she welcomes her Live Original Team. Listen in as they share the incredible story of how Live Original has been shaped behind the scenes. Be encouraged as team members discuss how their paths connected, how God has used four different women to join together as one united team, and how they have found the unexpected gift of friendship and sisterhood along the way.
